mic</strong> - Follow our heroes' misadventures as they piece the world back together again puzzle by puzzle<br></li><li><strong>Trophies </strong>- Earn in-game trophies and Steam achievements<br></li><li><strong>Art Gallery</strong> - See the art of Piczle up close and get a peek behind the scenes<br></li><li><strong>So many puzzles</strong> - 1100 puzzles for hour upon hour of addictive logic-puzzle fun<br></li><li><strong>Mouse &amp; controller input</strong> - Play as you like<br></li><li><strong>Fully localised in 9 languages</strong> - Play in English, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Italian, French, Japanese, traditional Chinese or simplified Chinese</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998790/extras/ad4afd6c6cd15dc1cb0fac17450b1928.apng?t=1729560187\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998790/extras/ad4afd6c6cd15dc1cb0fac17450b1928.poster.avif?t=1729560187\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=93 /></picture></span><br><br>50 puzzle packs (making <i>1000 </i>puzzles in total) cover a wide variety of themes<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sports<br></li><li>Japan<br></li><li>Mythical beasts<br></li><li>Boffins<br></li><li>Fantasy</li></ul>and <i>many </i>(45) more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/998790/extras/4dcb8981730a03e7846ab4aba83f26b6.avif?t=1729560187\" width=616 height=172 /></span><br><br>Puzzles range from a modest 20 by 20 grid squares all the way up to 64 by 64 and even 128 by 128 with difficulties from &quot;not very&quot; to &quot;extremely hard&quot;! The final pack, &quot;one color puzzles&quot; is in fact the most challenging set of puzzles in Piczle history: increasingly huge puzzles made up of entire one color. Can you solve them all?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akama